OL,3,CFire at former Water Edge Hotel in
OL,4,CBouley Bay
OL,6,FAll emergency services responded to a
OL,7,Ffire at the former Water Edge Hotel at
OL,8,FBouley Bay this morning (Saturday 28
OL,9,FMarch).
OL,11,FThe States of Jersey Police, ambulance
OL,12,Fstaff and the Fire and Rescue Service
OL,13,Fwere called to the site before 8am.
OL,15,FPolice officials have confirmed no one
OL,16,Fhas been injured, and an investigation
OL,17,Fis underway to determine the cause of
OL,18,Fthe incident.
