OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774897908
OL,3,CFire at former Water Edge Hotel in
OL,4,CBouley Bay
OL,6,FJersey's Fire and Rescue Services
OL,7,Freceived the call-out at 7:38 this
OL,8,Fmorning after reports of smoke from
OL,9,Fthe roof of the former hotel.
OL,11,FEight firefighters wearing breathing
OL,12,Fapparatus attended the scene, and two
OL,13,Fattacked the fire with a hose.
OL,15,FA Fire and Rescue spokesperson stated
OL,16,Fthat the cause is unknown and a site
OL,17,Finspection is underway.
